_sText: "It's early morning and the power lines hum peacefully in the mellow morning breeze...showtime for militant environmentalists that have been watching the dam for some time. Counter-Terrorists: Prevent the Militant Environmentalists from destroying the two critical points: the transformer loading bay and the center top of the dam. Terrorists: Destroy either critical point to cause a breach in the dam's structural integrity, thus allowing the river reclaim its natural course and beauty once more."
